snippet.title: Kainga: Seeds of Civilization - Developer Gameplay Walkthrough | gamescom 2021
snippet.description:
Take a look at this procedurally-generated rogue-like civ management sim with commentary from the sole developer,  Erik Rempen.

Thanks for checking out gamescom 2021 on IGN. Be sure to visit IGN from August 25th through August 27th for the daily gamescom 2021 stream to check out shows like gamescom Opening Night Live, gamescom Awesome Indies, gamescom Cosplay Contest, and gamescom Best of show. And for gamescom 2021 highlights, IGN will have them all. Throughout gamescom2021, we’ll be dropping new gamescom announcements, gamescom reveals, and gamescom trailers you don’t want to miss.

#IGN #gamescom2021
